s/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吃不到的葡萄是酸的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d0596e15ea7fe1bf2b3b7e1409c7a7bb378149","tid":775332,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1f685994c5d3b78f5734eef50b89a1502c6696","tid":775332,"uid":985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:24:23.000Z","msg":"同中五出黎考紀律部隊一樣，到你讀完非專業學位出黎，大家相差已經過百萬。<br />\n要追翻中五仔個收入差距同儲落既錢，一係你考到officer grade，一係你撈得好掂，40歲之前可以追平，撈得霉根本追唔到。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"真係要撈得掂<br />\n如果唔係差距只會愈嚟愈大<br />\n仲未計福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb4ec90fe1df498d0041a306f0baae8bb48b03e","tid":775332,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"叫人做判頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有出無入呀傻仔"},{"pid":"bd79a73bc360e86610ad3130681d00b732b72d73","tid":775332,"uid":151557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"移民先係正路"},{"pid":"70ca9b5625ef1e7bc369f33151be9f463515fd76","tid":775332,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eb4ec90fe1df498d0041a306f0baae8bb48b03e","tid":775332,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"叫人做判頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有出無入呀傻仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T17:56:36.000Z","msg":"收皮啦傻鳩<br />\n打死一世工啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1208a52115cc20153ff0a55884e83e6457fb79","tid":775332,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd79a73bc360e86610ad3130681d00b732b72d73","tid":775332,"uid":151557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"移民先係正路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T17:56:46.000Z","msg":"哪有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3205af980809338c3bdc604119612293ae8355d","tid":775332,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70ca9b5625ef1e7bc369f33151be9f463515fd76","tid":775332,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eb4ec90fe1df498d0041a306f0baae8bb48b03e","tid":775332,"uid":61207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"叫人做判頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有出無入呀傻仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T17:56:36.000Z","msg":"收皮啦傻鳩<br />\n打死一世工啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:28:28.000Z","msg":"好丫 一世做你既大老闆真係辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日就屌到你爆菊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c38d299fffc7e85d92a9e82bc5bd71752b9f50","tid":775332,"uid":63661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:30:38.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。<br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"}]}